<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=464143" target="top">Zeds</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=traxxeq>traxxeq</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 99<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/13/03 12:53:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4821.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: nod</span><hr size=1> I understand your problem, I use a Crafted Velium Warsword (10/18 no stats) and a GCM (11/20 with some dex and agi and 35 hp) and it seems to work fine keeping things pissed at me, only thing I would change is the GCM, i'd like to replace it with a frosty. I would sell the LSoEE and get somthing better for your offhand, and dps wise the defiance sucks, compared to what you could replace it with. The warsword's only 4k and the defiance 3k on my server. Or you could go cheaper and sell the LSoEE and get a Blade of the Green Dragon Eye, its 13/24. Damn nice for offhand and its like 1k, and you would have all that pp from the LSoEE to get a kickass mainhand. Good luck with whatever you decide.<br>
